sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant API Server
    participant Unit Controller
    participant Scheduler
    participant Kubelet
    participant Unit Agent

    User->>API Server: Create Unit
    API Server-->>User: Confirm creation

    Unit Controller->>API Server: Watch Unit changes
    API Server-->>Unit Controller: Notify new Unit

    alt Deletion in progress
        Unit Controller->>Unit Controller: Handle finalizers (delete Pod, PVC)
    end

    Unit Controller->>API Server: Create PVCs

    Unit Controller->>Unit Controller: Update Unit status

    Unit Controller->>Unit Controller: Auto-recovery (if pod failed)

    Unit Controller->>API Server: Create Pod
    Note over Unit Controller: Pod owned by Unit via OwnerReference

    Scheduler->>API Server: Watch unscheduled Pods
    API Server-->>Scheduler: Notify new Pod
    Scheduler->>API Server: Assign node to Pod

    Kubelet->>API Server: Watch Pod assigned to this node
    API Server-->>Kubelet: Notify Pod assignment

    Kubelet->>Kubelet: Create containers

    Kubelet->>API Server: Update Pod Status

    Unit Controller->>API Server: Watch Pod status
    Unit Controller->>Unit Controller: Update Unit status

    Unit Controller->>Unit Agent: Load unit config (via gRPC)
    Unit Agent-->>Unit Controller: Config loaded

    Unit Controller->>Unit Agent: Start service process (via gRPC)
    Unit Agent-->>Unit Controller: Service started

    Unit Controller->>Unit Controller: Final Unit status update
